{"type": "article", "id": 15826, "title": "120 年前的旧居改造，亮点是能捕捉光影变化的隐形窗户", "description": "废弃的老旧仓库也可以做成一个有情调的休息室", "date": "2015-10-10T08:10:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13850, "name": "房屋改造"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 16911, "name": "Ryo Matsui"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 193, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070217292484PREtLXmruGxgjV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>来自东京的建筑事务所 </span><span>Ryo Matsui </span>承接了这块位于守谷的地，它原本是一间有 <span>120 </span>年历史的仓库，但因为地震受到了严重破坏。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t重新修建时保留了仓库像盒子一样的结构，方正封闭。屋顶采用传统日式建筑中切妻造，即悬山式，呈现出两个坡面的顶，并将屋檐悬伸在山墙以外，是曾经应用广泛的民居屋顶。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172917xLsYiVDS27tpwh1j.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"959\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.17237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172917jAnwVgR3yITCbqFx.jpg\" width=\"387\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49870801\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172918uSEx63aTGAKHhNpF.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1063\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.299511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t重建时还运用了很多当代的设计，比如将墙面上有带穿孔的砖漆成白色。房子内部的墙上其实开了许多高低错落的窗户，但外面的砖块并没有因此而空出来。所以，从外面看起来依然是一个封闭的盒子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t白天，光线能透过穿孔的砖块照进屋子里，到了晚上，屋里点上灯，就能从外面看到屋里的光，像纸糊的灯笼，或是隔了一扇屏风，有一种朦胧美。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172918RPa2n89EOS1wDI5j.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1029\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t即便是在夜晚也很难发现这些都是窗户。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172919sNpH8enBh3xYv5ZL.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66724138\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t窗户隐藏在房子里，随着内外光线的强弱变化显现出来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172919bx4wN9egQaAqMOlX.jpg\" width=\"864\" height=\"588\" title=\"白天与夜晚，显隐两种窗户\" alt=\"白天与夜晚，显隐两种窗户\" data-ratio=\"0.68055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>白天与夜晚，显隐两种窗户</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t屋内也是典型的日式风格，统一使用浅色系的木质家具。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172920xLBqEVMben167k8W.jpg\" width=\"473\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22621564\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">窗户旁边搭建了一个小夹层，从楼梯上去，是个看书发呆的地方</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172920v5e8ANduPyUOZQqb.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1061\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">屋顶的木梁下吊着几盏灯，刚好在窗户的位置。让光线能直接透出去。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172921e9TX8kHZGPrwoz7u.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"916\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1198044\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172921NJEcsgVxaUSefhYZ.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"588\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172922YANwvcRDhTFgn8OJ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\"带酒窖的地下室\" alt=\"带酒窖的地下室\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>带酒窖的地下室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t真正的住宅在这所房子的旁边，这边是庭院里喝茶休息的地方。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021729226BFi9kCfam7TNogr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" 左边是真正的住宅\" alt=\" 左边是真正的住宅\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> 左边是住宅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172923cZJRlENwigk6XPt4.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\"厨房\" alt=\"厨房\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>厨房</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172924n6yDkNf7RhpHFUcQ.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"386\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66551724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/ryo-matsui-architects-rebirth-house-moriya-japan-10-08-2015/\" target=\"_blank\"> designboom</a> 和<a href=\"http://www.matsui-architects.com/works/rebirthhouse/#gallery\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"http://www.matsui-architects.com/works/rebirthhouse/#gallery\" target=\"_blank\">Ryo Matsui  </a>主页</span> \r\n</p>\n\n"}